Package: pdlyr
Title: Compatibility package to access both plyr and dplyr
Version: 0.0-3
Authors@R: as.person("Kirill MÃ¼ller <krlmlr+r@mailbox.org> [aut, cre]")
Description: This package aims at simplifying the transition
  from plyr to dplyr by providing suitable wrapper methods
  for the few incompatible overlaps.
